        <h3>Jeff Galloway</h3>
        <p>
          US Olympian (Munich 1972) and creator of the Run Walk Run method. He has coached
          thousands of beginner runners with scheduled walk breaks — and maintains that walk
          breaks can almost eliminate injuries in beginners.
        </p>
        <a class="card-source" href="https://www.jeffgalloway.com/training/run-walk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source: jeffgalloway.com ↗</a>
      </article>
